Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Assigned' to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average resolution time of 'Accepted + Assigned' for cases involving 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Assigned and activity Completed + In Call for cases where activity Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Total time spent in 'Accepted + Assigned' before transitioning to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Minimum time from 'Accepted + Assigned' to 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average time it takes 'Accepted + Assigned' to be followed by 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Total resolution time of 'Accepted + Assigned' in cases ending with 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Minimum time it takes 'Accepted + Assigned' to be done before 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Assigned' to 'Accepted + In Progress' across all variants
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Total time for 'Accepted + Assigned' in variants leading to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average time for 'Accepted + Assigned' in cases that pass through 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' before completion
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and the end of case where activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor occurs

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'Accepted + Assigned' in processes involving 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Assigned and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Assigned' to 'Completed + Resolved', considering only the fastest variant paths
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total time from 'Accepted + Assigned' to 'Completed + In Call', considering all occurrences in the log
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average time to transition from 'Accepted + Assigned' to any subsequent activity, highlighting the impact on the process flow
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Assigned and the end of the case

Name: Total time for 'Accepted + Assigned' across different countries, as specified in the event log
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country

Name: Minimum time from 'Accepted + Assigned' to 'Completed + Resolved' in the most efficient process variant
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average time for 'Accepted + Assigned' before reaching 'Accepted + Wait', comparing the duration to reach 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Accepted + Wait'
